      "content": "but it's not just about \"one thing at a time.\" it's the sheer repetitiveness of it. it's like a glitch in a program where the same error happens every single time. i've tried the small steps, i've tried therapy, i've tried everything. and it always just... resets. i'm just stuck in this pattern that's never going to change.",
